{"tid":1515082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢兩個幾月，我有好多疑問","createTime":"2019-08-29T03:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T08:48:43.000Z","uid":205462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffbcc148e68eeb3fba2b7ad5069bad3fea27dee6","tid":1515082,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:56:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我啱啱放監出嚟，都有follow呢場運動，有好多嘢想請教大家<br />\n<br />\n1) 6月初嘅時候，含莖長官同劣政屍屍長，分別話因為修改逃犯條例而收到電話恐嚇，但警方一直無公佈調查進度 (反而較近期嘅起底，已開始進行拘捕)，是否刻意隱瞞有人報假案呢?<br />\n<br />\n2) 有不少圖片及消息，顯示警隊混入咗不少非本港執法部門嘅人員，如果屬實，咁佢哋係唔係違反咗逗留條件呢 (即係做黑工)? 點解入境處一直無行動 / 公開闢謠呢?<br />\n<br />\n3) 近日，在網上流傳好多圖片，有一啲係話示威者扮成警方，喺長洲進行特訓 (已由有關區議員證實係虛假消息)，散播該虛假消息嘅人等，可能已干犯&lt;&lt;公安條例&gt;&gt;(Cap. 245), 為何警方尚未作出任何調查行動?<br />\n<br />\n再續"},{"pid":"8196f6bf8f24a481d404bde4019835c32e7fe595","tid":1515082,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:12:35.000Z","msg":"反送中TOMMY阮民安男神IG直升！繼續推！未follow快啲！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1515079\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1515079</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n推post既時候聽下歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始戀愛<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2GbVOdXbqIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2GbVOdXbqIQ&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=738e95e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2GbVOdXbqIQ</a><br />\n<br />\n終止戀愛<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ck6cdBuI0qM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fck6cdBuI0qM&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=fe362a6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ck6cdBuI0qM</a>"},{"pid":"e33d355107faca63243816bd6848851f13a9e742","tid":1515082,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:21:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>